articles.title: The P7 peptide antagonizes bFGF-induced malignant behaviors of ovarian cancer by inhibiting MEK/ERK signaling pathway.
articles.summary: P7 peptide effectively blocks basic fibroblast growth factor's ability to promote ovarian cancer cell growth and spread by interrupting a key cellular signaling pathway.
